title: How to get warranty support for pixel 5 in Finland
content:
Hi all, my pixel 5 is having constant USB issues. Tried inspecting and cleaning the port, but didn't help.

My issue: i can't find any way to contact support to file a claim. Tried chatting, but the option never appears. It's 1pm here in Finland, so I'd expect some european team to be online.

For context: bought the phone in France, but now living in Finland. Still under warranty.

Thanks.
